<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَمِنْهُ:</span> <span class="c3">{لَا أُقْسِمُ}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span>: أَيْ -أُقْسِمُ،<span class="c5"> وَتُقْرَأُ:</span> <span class="c3">{لَأُقْسِمُ}</span>،<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{وَقَاسَمَهُمَا}</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span>: " حَلَفَ لَهُمَا , وَلَمْ يَحْلِفَا لَهُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> <span class="c3">{تَقَاسَمُوا}</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span>: تَحَالَفُوا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
